{"id": "2708", "post": "<div class=\"post-2708 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-avantehosting-net tag-florida tag-kvm tag-orlando tag-usa tag-xen tag-yearly\" id=\"post-2708\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/avante-hosting-6half-yearly-128mb-kvm-or-xen-in-florida-usa/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Avante Hosting \u2013 $6/Half-Yearly 128MB KVM or XEN in Florida, USA</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/avantehosting-net/\" rel=\"tag\">avantehosting.net</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/florida/\" rel=\"tag\">florida</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/kvm/\" rel=\"tag\">kvm</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/orlando/\" rel=\"tag\">orlando</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/usa/\" rel=\"tag\">USA</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/xen/\" rel=\"tag\">xen</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/yearly/\" rel=\"tag\">yearly</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> July 8, 2012 @ 9:57 am, by Chief</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"http://www.avantehosting.net\" title=\"Avante Hosting\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/avantehosting.jpg.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/avantehosting.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"avantehosting\" width=\"300\" height=\"197\" class=\"screenshot litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></a>Chris from <em><a href=\"http://www.avantehosting.net\" title=\"Avante Hosting\" target=\"_blank\">Avante Hosting</a></em> has sent us a nice collection of KVM and XEN plans that are available on new E3-1230 Version 2\u2019s. We are really pleased to be seeing first time hosts to LowEndBox offering more than just OpenVZ\u2019s and the following plans are no exception.</p><table><tbody><tr><td>\n<strong>KVM/XEN Plastic VPS</strong><p></p><ul><li>128MB Dedicated Ram</li><li>6GB Diskspace</li><li>62GB Bandwidth</li><li>1Gbit Port</li><li>1x IPv4 Address</li><li>1x CPU Core Access</li><li>SolusVM/XEN</li><li>$6.00/Half-Year, $12.00/Year</li><li><strong>Signup: </strong><a href=\"https://clients.avantehosting.net/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=184\" title=\"Avante Hosting Signup\" target=\"_blank\">XEN</a> | <a href=\"https://clients.avantehosting.net/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=208\" title=\"Avante Hosting Signup\" target=\"_blank\">KVM</a></li></ul></td><td>\n<strong>KVM/XEN Tin VPS</strong><p></p><ul><li>256MB Dedicated Ram</li><li>12GB Diskspace</li><li>125GB Bandwidth</li><li>1Gbit Port</li><li>1x IPv4 Address</li><li>1x CPU Core Access</li><li>SolusVM/XEN</li><li>$6.00/Quarter, $12.00/Half-Year</li><li><strong>Signup: </strong><a href=\"https://clients.avantehosting.net/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=183\" title=\"Avante Hosting Signup\" target=\"_blank\">XEN</a> | <a href=\"https://clients.avantehosting.net/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=207\" title=\"Avante Hosting Signup\" target=\"_blank\">KVM</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p><em>Avante Hosting</em> own all of their equipment and colocate with HostDime in Florida. All nodes now consist of E3-1230 Version 2\u2019s, Raid10 with 1Gbit connections to each node. They currently peer with Tiscali, Level3, Savvis and Global Crossing via a 10Gbit backbone. IPV6 is currently not offered however Chris informs us it is coming as soon as Arin approves their /32 IPv6 subnet. You can order up to an additional 10 IPv4 for your VPS at $2/IP up to 10, beyond 10 you will need to submit a ticket and justify the use.<br>\n<span id=\"more-2708\"></span><br>\nPayment via Paypal, Liberty Reserve and Credit Card is accepted and covered by a 3 day refund policy. Wire/Bank transfer for orders over $100 can also be arranged however you must cover the bank fees associated with the transfers. They run an EV SSL on their main website and are a registered Canadian company operating out of Toronto Ontario, Canada.</p><p><strong>KVM/XEN Copper VPS</strong></p><ul><li>512MB Dedicated Ram</li><li>25GB Diskspace</li><li>250GB Bandwidth</li><li>1Gbit Port</li><li>1x IPv4 Address</li><li>1x CPU Core Access</li><li>SolusVM/XEN</li><li>$4.00/Month, $12.00/Quarter</li><li><strong>Signup: </strong><a href=\"https://clients.avantehosting.net/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=182\" title=\"Avante Hosting Signup\" target=\"_blank\">XEN</a> | <a href=\"https://clients.avantehosting.net/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=206\" title=\"Avante Hosting Signup\" target=\"_blank\">KVM</a></li></ul><p><strong>Test Files &amp; IPs</strong><br>\n<strong>IP: </strong>198.136.62.133<br>\n<strong>Test File: </strong>http://198.136.62.133/100mb.test</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Favante-hosting-6half-yearly-128mb-kvm-or-xen-in-florida-usa%2F&amp;t=Avante%20Hosting%20-%20%246%2FHalf-Yearly%20128MB%20KVM%20or%20XEN%20in%20Florida%2C%20USA\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Avante%20Hosting%20-%20%